Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:42.86,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,STASIUN KICHIJOJI
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.63,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,THE INVISIBLE MAN AND HIS SOON-TO-BE WIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:38.07,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,THE INVISIBLE MAN AND HIS SOON-TO-BE WIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:43.78,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,TUTUP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:50.91,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,STASIUN KICHIJOJI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.67,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,LIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:02.06,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,KARMA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:40.21,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,"EPISODE 12: AKHIRNYA"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:41.04,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,TAMAT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.76,0:00:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, pada dasarnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau mencari kakaknya yang lama hilang?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Itu permintaan klien kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka terpisah sejak masih sangat kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, mereka akhirnya bertemu lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, syukurlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu. Lalu, untuk apa cincin itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kenang-kenangan dari orang tua mereka\Nyang hilang saat mereka kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakaknya menyimpan cincin ibunya,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan adiknya menyimpan pin dasi ayah mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu menjadi bukti bahwa mereka bersaudara.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial. Ceritanya bagus juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kenapa kalian membuntutiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.78,0:00:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kau sadar, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar, sudah kubilang dia pasti sadar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf sekali kami mengganggu pekerjaanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak. Kupikir Futa sedang menilaiku,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa aku pantas menjalin hubungan\Ndenganmu, Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Apa dia sedang mengawasiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus menyelesaikan tugas klien\Ndan membuktikan kemampuanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cukup gugup soal itu.\NApa ada alasan lain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, diamlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Intinya, kalau kau sampai\Nmengkhianati Kakak,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan kuhancurkan kepalamu\Ndengan pemukul ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersiaplah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.72,0:01:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemukul itu terbuat dari plastik, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?! Pemukul?! Pemukul apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Kau tidak menginap malam ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menginap di warnet malam ini\Ndan jalan-jalan besok sebelum pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian mau mampir ke tempatku?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yakin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:02:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Ruangnya cukup untuk kita bertiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa kau benar-benar yakin, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Futa, kau tidak perlu mengkhawatirkan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak usah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah... Begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin lain kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, silakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Futa, ayolah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dia dan Kakak menikah,\Nkami akan jadi keluarga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak tahu apa pun tentangnya\Nselain pekerjaannya sebagai detektif.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggan berkeluarga dengan orang\Nyang wajahnya tak bisa kulihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Kakak tidak peduli soal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sikapnya sama saja seperti di rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jaga Kakakku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi. Aku membuatkan sarapan.\NTinggal hangatkan di microwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kira-kira Akira membuatkan apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah! Akira membuatkanku roti panggang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya juga tidak terlalu manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira kerja pagi ini, tapi besok dia libur.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti ada di sekitar sini... Wortel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, ini kentang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bumbunya ada di sini...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, apa sebaiknya\Naku tak usah masak makan malam?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak. Aku baru pulang,\Ndan kau sudah memasak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.39,0:04:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau membuatkan sarapan untukku, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau melakukannya di tempatku\Ntanpa izin. Itu alasan utamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya seperti kita sudah menikah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Aku baru sadar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai kapan aku akan terus\Ntersipu karena hal-hal kecil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menerima surel dari\Npengelola apartemenku hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa sewaku akan segera habis,\Njadi aku harus segera pindah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kita harus buru-buru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sudah memilih apartemen\Ndengan sangat hati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak banyak yang memenuhi\Nsemua kriteria kita...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi menginap di sini sangat menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saja apartemenku kecil,\Njadi kita sering menginap di tempatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau ingin menunda tinggal bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Aku ingin sekali tinggal bersama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saja...\Naku sudah terbiasa dengan tempat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, meski pindah ke apartemen baru\Nitu menyenangkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}rasanya agak menyedihkan juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kau tinggal di apartemenku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita tak perlu repot\Nmencari apartemen baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari luangkan waktu untuk mengemas\Nbarang-barang di tempatmu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan memindahkannya ke apartemenku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu keputusan yang sangat mudah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pilihan itu juga sudah ada sejak awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian akan tinggal bareng\Ndi tempat Tonome? Akhirnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya terwujud juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sedang bersiap-siap untuk pindah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beri tahu aku kalau kalian butuh bantuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa mengangkut barang\Nke tempat Tonome dengan mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah! Luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini gampang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenagamu kuat sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Tonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski dia pamer tenaga begitu,\Nmau kucarikan mobil van untuk pindahan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh! Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang di Elf Garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami mencari teh hitam\Nuntuk dijadikan hadiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja. Aku rekomendasikan yang ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, bagaimana kabar istrimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah lama kami tidak melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba ruangannya jadi gelap...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak meninggalkanku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa... Karma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa! Istrimu akan pulang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silau sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar aku yang bawa barang berat!\NTaruh saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Te-Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, mundurlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mundur?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedikit lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedikit lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, sempurna!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari jarak sejauh ini,\Nkutukanku tak akan memengaruhimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menerima berkat\Ndari semua elf putih di hutan suci.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kutukan elf gelap rendahan\Ntak akan mempan padaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi berhentilah mengeluh\Ndan oleskan krim antiguratan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ta-Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan! Jangan remehkan\Nkekuatan para elf putih...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Light? Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kontraksi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Tiba-tiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia akan segera melahirkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi bukankah HPL-nya masih agak lama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sampai panik saking kagetnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa yang harus kulakukan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Light! Bayi kita! Jangan mati!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenanglah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hubungi ayah dan rumah sakit sekarang juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, ambil tas bersalinku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karma, satu rahasia lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kembar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar. Dia sengaja merahasiakannya\Nsebagai kejutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kau\Ntidak terlalu senang mendengarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, sepertinya ada cangkir\Nyang jatuh dari rak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah begini sejak Light\Nberangkat ke rumah sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat mencemaskan persalinannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi kutukanku terus-menerus\Nmengalir keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Apa ini akan jadi\Npersalinan yang sulit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seluruh klan Light ada di rumah sakit\Nuntuk membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir semuanya akan baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seluruh klannya ada di sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Elf putih melahirkan\Nsambil menerima berkat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, jika terjadi sesuatu pada Light\Natau bayi kami karena kutukanku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karma, itu alasanmu\Nmengundang kami ke toko hari ini
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk memindahkan sebagian kutukanmu\Npada kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Kalian sudah sadar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita pulang sekarang juga, Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu! Aku tak sanggup menanggung\Nkutukan ini sendirian!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paham kau sangat khawatir,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi bisakah kau melampiaskan kutukanmu\Nseperti waktu itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kecemasan sebesar ini, pelampiasanku\Ntak bisa mengimbanginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:11:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berbagilah beban ini denganku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak perlu melibatkan Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa salahnya memindahkan kutukanku\Npada orang lain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jelas itu salah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini persalinan pertamanya,\Ndan anak kembar pula.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus membantu\Nmengurangi kecemasannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau menemani Karma sebentar saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, kau baik sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahaya kalau ada barang jatuh lagi.\NTetaplah di sisiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Y-Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karma, lepaskan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?! Kau baik-baik saja?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa wastafel\Njatuh menimpa kepalaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah aku bisa membujuk Shizuka\Nuntuk pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Elus, elus...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau menempel terus padaku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau begini terus sepanjang hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kita ke tempatmu, 'kan?\NMau mampir beli sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?! Kau mau ke tempatku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak usah malu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Tunggu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi bagaimana caranya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Karma tidak ada di sini...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Sepertinya kutukanku\Nmenular padamu, Tonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?! Tapi aku tak merasakan\Nperbedaan apa pun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Reaksinya lebih cepat dari dugaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hanya memindahkan kutukan itu padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong hilangkan sekarang juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kenapa kau pikir\Naku bisa melakukannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ini elf gelap yang terkutuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau bertingkah seolah ini salahku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan kutukannya akan hilang?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:13:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah jelas!\NSaat semua kegelisahanku hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Intinya, saat bayi kami\Nlahir dengan selamat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Dari rumah sakit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka memanggilku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, dari Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pasti tak sabar melihat\Nanak-anakmu lahir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh... Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}S-Sampai jumpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar. Aku akan segera melihat mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makin dipikirkan, makin cemas...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Light! Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baik. Pemberian berkatnya sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau akan segera datang?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka akan segera lahir, tapi kutukanku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau masih membahas itu?\NKarma, tolong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak sanggup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bilang tak masalah,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi jika sesuatu terjadi pada kalian\Nkarena ulahku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menangis?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf... aku sangat tidak berguna...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa berbuat apa-apa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar, aku tak memintamu\Nmelakukan apa pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma ingin kau ada bersamaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karma! Datang dan temani aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Light, apa kau menangis juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebab... Sebab...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga sangat cemas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:15:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bayi kita juga menunggumu, Bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhenti murung dan cepat datang ke sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan ke sana sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku janji tak akan kabur lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, Kikira akan tiba nanti malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, aku akan membuang\Npiring-piring tak terpakai ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}K-Kau baik-baik saja?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Ini berbahaya, jangan mendekat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua selotipnya terlepas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pasti karena kutukan Karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karma bilang dia menularkan\Nkutukannya padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya, kesialan akan terjadi meski\NKarma tak ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tapi sepertinya hanya kesialan kecil,\Ntak lebih.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai aku tak pulang dan\Nmenemanimu lebih lama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak, aku tak mau kau\Nterlibat dalam hal ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin melindungimu dari bahaya, Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa ada wastafel lain yang menimpaku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh! Maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.\NNiatku datang untuk membantu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf! Ini gara-gara aku memintamu\Nmenemani Karma sementara...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akibatnya, kau malah menderita\Nsaat membantuku pindahan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, ini karena kutukan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Piring jatuh dan melukaimu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kau tak harus membantuku,\Nkutukannya mungkin tak seburuk ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira, pulang dan istirahatlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pindahanku, aku akan berusaha sendiri\Nsampai Kikira tiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, ucapanmu membuatku sedih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama ini aku sudah berusaha keras\Nuntuk menahanmu di sisiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, itu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, tolong jangan menjauhkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku takkan pernah melakukan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau hubungan kita merenggang\Ngara-gara Karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku setuju soal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kutukan itu takkan menular\Ndarimu kepadaku, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku tak terpengaruh kutukan itu,\Njika aku ada di atasmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin tak ada kesialan\Nyang akan menimpamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasakan, kutukan bodoh!\NKau tak bisa melukainya sekarang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada apa pun yang terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin cara ini berhasil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sh-Shizuka, aku tak bisa bernapas...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}M-Maafkan aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya? Halo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, anak-anakku! Si kembar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka lahir dengan selamat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah? Selamat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kutukanmu tak menimbulkan masalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya sehat dan bahagia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itu kabar bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang sekali bisa datang melihat\NLight dan bayi-bayi kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tak ada bantuanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kutukanku pasti sangat memberatkan\Ndan menghancurkanku sebelum tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau memang andalanku\Nsaat aku dilanda masalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya itu jadi masalah besar bagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah semuanya sehat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, dan sepertinya kutukan itu\Nsudah hilang sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, masuk akal juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kutukan itu sudah hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa tak ada gunanya lagi\Nmenempel padamu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi syukurlah kutukannya sudah lenyap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat senang\Nkau melindungiku, Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:19:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei. Aku datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami agak terlambat berkemas\Nkarena beberapa kendala.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa. Aku memang berniat membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang bertemu denganmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Madaraito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kata Daichi, kalian mungkin\Nbutuh tambahan tenaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, kalian semua ada di sini!\NTerima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana barangnya?\NBiar aku bawa yang sudah siap angkut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita dibantu oleh orang-orang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fiuh. Ya, semuanya sudah beres.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya lancar berkat bantuan semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Mari mulai bongkar barang\Nsesuai kebutuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, saking sibuknya hari ini,\Nkita sampai lupa makan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau pesan piza\Nuntuk pesta pindahan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Piza!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sudah bekerja keras untuk pindahan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.51,0:21:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya dimulai juga!\NKita tinggal bersama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada sesuatu yang ingin kuberikan padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Memberiku sesuatu... sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cincin?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.66,0:22:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sudah bertemu\Norang tua masing-masing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, kau terlalu terburu-buru lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah... bisakah kau ulurkan\Ntangan kirimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?! Tangan kiriku?! Jangan-jangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.86,0:22:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kunci apartemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.53,0:22:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kunci apartemen kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.51,0:22:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira dan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hitung-hitung latihan, tak ada salahnya\Nmembuat kunci cadangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.54,0:22:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:22:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira, aku mencintaimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin coba pakai kuncinya,\Njadi aku mau keluar sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.07,0:23:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ide bagus. Bagaimana kalau kita\Npergi beli makanan penutup?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.73,0:23:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.21,0:23:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jalan-jalan cari pencuci mulut\Nsebagai perayaan! Beli apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertanyaan bagus. Belakangan ini\Nmakanan penutup di toko sangat lezat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru-baru ini kau makan apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Krep pisang cokelat.
